{"id": 2542, "genre": 1001, "title": "小时候哪些爸妈替你做过的决定，现在想想其实挺不合理的？", "description": "小孩子没有完全自己做主的能力，但有些事情总该有个商量的过程。（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA Images ）", "record_count": 3566, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180926153456UxCvyzjgaFMSsJXu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-31T03:00:29Z", "options": [{"id": 325632, "content": "替我安排兴趣爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496460}, {"id": 326144, "content": "没让我去跳舞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574684}, {"id": 325635, "content": "红包先帮我存着以后再给我", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572511}, {"id": 327427, "content": "放在亲戚家寄养", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583467}, {"id": 325636, "content": "总用伤害来掩饰爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273317}, {"id": 325637, "content": "忘记了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487564}, {"id": 325638, "content": "基本上没有……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557514}, {"id": 325639, "content": "13753179728", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572524}, {"id": 325641, "content": "13753179728772371752", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572524}, {"id": 325642, "content": "怕我到社会上伺候不好领导，所以让我在家里就受尽伺候不好领导的后果", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572530}, {"id": 325643, "content": "“不用玩了，以后玩的机会多得是…”\n以后…", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957827}, {"id": 325644, "content": "从不让我做决定。问我意见就是走个过场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555639}, {"id": 325645, "content": "自己没出息自我放弃却硬要我努力🙃", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563432}, {"id": 325646, "content": "母胎solo那么多年那位，假设你的娃娃亲对象喜欢的人不是你，那么你会不会继续羡慕有娃娃亲嘞…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957827}, {"id": 325647, "content": "把她觉得没价值的东西给扔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567200}, {"id": 325648, "content": "给我起了个“随性”的名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1268443}, {"id": 325649, "content": "他比你小，你就是要让着他的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572559}, {"id": 325650, "content": "让我留级", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571486}, {"id": 325651, "content": "不让我同别的小朋友玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568682}, {"id": 325652, "content": "因为年代的原因思想和主流价值观格格不入", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913171}, {"id": 325653, "content": "上学可以改变命运，切╮（╯＿╰）╭", "image": "img/option/option/201901312209546WRPCuZi20b9QqDS", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238281}, {"id": 325655, "content": "认为他们是对我好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446715}, {"id": 325656, "content": "禁止我接触任何电子娱乐产品😨", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507086}, {"id": 325657, "content": "不在我身边", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572587}, {"id": 325658, "content": "我这都是为你好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572593}, {"id": 325660, "content": "让我学画画", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572628}, {"id": 326173, "content": "还没有，我觉得父母说的都很对，可惜我听取明白得太晚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573054}, {"id": 325662, "content": "沒有讓我多去接觸不一樣的新事物，不允許我去接觸和學習我提出感興趣的愛好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570815}, {"id": 325664, "content": "口口声声为你好，却做出你不喜欢的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572650}, {"id": 325666, "content": "买了我觉得很丑的鞋或者衣服，我可能就当时穿了吧，然后再也没穿过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565204}, {"id": 325669, "content": "让我学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571745}, {"id": 325670, "content": "让我在国外长大", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851003}, {"id": 325671, "content": "这个不行那个不行，胆子小，嘴笨", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528683}, {"id": 325672, "content": "我妈从小有一个跳拉丁舞的梦。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440600}, {"id": 325673, "content": "，，，都是为了你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1509413}, {"id": 329770, "content": "你们找个日子结婚吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 325674, "content": "很凶地去游戏机室找我骂我，尽管我的成绩一直排前一二名", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1401953}, {"id": 325675, "content": "\n天生抵触替我做的一切决定，不光小时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423415}, {"id": 326699, "content": "我现在这么没自信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219371}, {"id": 325677, "content": "中学为了不影响学习，阻断我跟几个关系很好的朋友，只因为他们不学习天天出去玩…现在都混得风生水起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886727}, {"id": 325678, "content": "让我学画画", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572744}, {"id": 325679, "content": "额", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434148}, {"id": 325935, "content": "我因为小任性放弃的兴趣特长，我妈居然真的就让我放弃了😂现在想想还挺希望她那个时候打我逼我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568370}, {"id": 325680, "content": "都没错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097856}, {"id": 325682, "content": "都是为了你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1514618}, {"id": 325683, "content": "只能跟成绩好的玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572815}, {"id": 325684, "content": "把我的日记本撬开来看还美名其曰是关心我", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572828}, {"id": 325944, "content": "多和成绩好的玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553187}, {"id": 325697, "content": "觉得我学习不好，让我放弃舞蹈去上补习班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572256}, {"id": 326466, "content": "带我去游戏厅，他喝茶，我打游戏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576861}]}